{"tid":977316,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"前些日子，有位匿名人士說要讓一般人知道知道“Comic Market 的現實”。","createTime":"2019-01-11T05:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T07:26:55.000Z","uid":150609,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b500646df9d9a2f1939cfdfcbf5c7afd2ea2fb","tid":977316,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"此人首次作為出展社團參加了 Comiket，但完全沒有收穫到喜悅，體驗到的只有痛苦。他認為，官方宣傳稿裡只會寫正面意見，像他這種負面意見會被無視，所以就用這種方式發佈出來。<br />\n<br />\n他預測會有&ldquo;想向 Comiket 獻媚的業者&rdquo;對他群起而攻，還在推文整合裡特意標上了一句&ldquo;因為是親身體驗所以禁止過度批評&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n那麼，這人到底在 Comiket 上遭遇了什麼呢？答案很簡單：他的同人誌，一本都沒賣出去。<br />\n<br />\n他憤憤不平地指責，一般來說，運營難道不是應該照顧第一次參加的社團，派個託來買上那麼一本嗎？可是完全沒有這種關照。<br />\n<br />\n他接連發了十多條推文，抨擊：如今的 Comiket 已經不是原先的那個 Comiket 了，能賣出去的，<strong>只有專業作家和&ldquo;把動畫、漫畫改造成色情漫畫的玩意&rdquo;</strong>。Comiket 成了一個&ldquo;空有其名的賣色情漫畫的活動&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnWp4ez.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnWp4ez.jpg&h=4a3babb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncomiket真係變哂質  變成大手 專業作家 商業攤 賣咸書既地方<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Txdc7o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Txdc7o.gif&h=1d4bd5ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般人動漫愛好者 互相交流風氣已不存在<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPO4jNx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPO4jNx.gif&h=9acbef28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><br />\n链接：<a href=\"http://www.anitama.cn/article/cfb9cf8248a18d35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.anitama.cn%2Farticle%2Fcfb9cf8248a18d35&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=1a568c8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.anitama.cn/article/cfb9cf8248a18d35</a><br />\n来源：Anitama<br />\n</div></span>"},{"pid":"c78caa5d8d80a1ce5df6671e04f510b025f0dafc","tid":977316,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"我一開始就以為comiket係賣咸濕同人既地方<br />\n所以無誤會~"},{"pid":"f3ecb888b6e8c592883a8a2c2d3db4ebbf061cc1","tid":977316,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要？"},{"pid":"ab41e44656e1f3e476788846d7300cd7a137f92c","tid":977316,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"一入場就排大手買咸書，買完咸書就排商業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1060a3852e989d3e3cecd09b4bfa6b195035c51a","tid":977316,"uid":2223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"其實第一次參展賣唔出好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deff3e669e29679aeadb23398c19a3137bfeb410","tid":977316,"uid":106247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"技不如人賣唔出好出奇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1394e5cca047f3113b712dd213761b417dea5c8d","tid":977316,"uid":115042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:26:55.000Z","msg":"去過一次CM,同人區有ｄ學術性，資訊性嘅書同攤位，但老實講我去都係買本子，<br />\n或者劃個專區只賣18禁會好ｄ"}]}